  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multi center study to evaluate the safety of the AMENDTM Mitral Valve Repair System and its
      ability to reduce mitral regurgitation. AMEND device is an annuloplasty ring implanted in a
      minimally invasive trans-catheter method.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
